considered_outliers_hash_map = dict() #considered_outliers_set = set()


# 
for feature in log_data.keys():
    
    data_of_feature = log_data[feature]
    
    # TODOQ125th
    Q1 = np.percentile(data_of_feature, 25)
    
    # TODOQ375th
    Q3 = np.percentile(data_of_feature, 75)
    
    # TODO1.5
    step = Q3 - Q1
    
    # 
    print "Data points considered outliers for the feature '{}':".format(feature)
    considered_outliers = log_data[~((log_data[feature] >= Q1 - step) & (log_data[feature] <= Q3 + step))]
#     print considered_outliers.index
#     considered_outliers_set |= set(considered_outliers.index)
    for i in considered_outliers.index:
        if i in considered_outliers_hash_map :
            considered_outliers_hash_map[i] = considered_outliers_hash_map[i] + 1
        else :
            considered_outliers_hash_map[i] = 1
    display(considered_outliers)
